{"tid":1750290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[V仔]泰亨驚現票站！！！","createTime":"2019-11-24T10:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T11:55:35.000Z","uid":199592,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3231eca0a80aeedb015910ff687efb347dea6e","tid":1750290,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【監察選舉】區議會選舉星期日舉行，為調查每個票站的運作情況，我們需要大眾幫忙，收集全港610個票站每小時的投票人數紀錄，以便進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n這種調查方法，傳真社於2016年的立法會選舉曾經使用，當日在96個收集到的票站紀錄，有5個票站被發現投票人數與點算出來的票數不符，雖然追查下事件最終無可疑，但監察到的票站只佔總數六分一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/factwire_DCelection2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffactwire_DCelection2019&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=57cbd282\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/factwire_DCelection2019</a><br />\n<br />\n截至 11月24日 17:40<br />\n以下為仍未有人認頭票站<br />\n<br />\n**各位仍可重複認頭未在下方列出的票站。謝謝幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n香港島：<br />\nA0402德瑞國際學校山頂校舍 <br />\n<br />\nB1101瑪利曼中學 <br />\nB1102香港青少年服務處成和青少年中心<br />\n<br />\nD1601南島中學 <br />\nD1602香港國際學校 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九龍：<br />\nF1202海盈邨平台乒乓球場<br />\n<br />\nJ1302竹園區神召會好鄰舍家庭中心 <br />\n<br />\n新界：<br />\nK1202澳仙納幼稚園舊址<br />\nK1701香港道教聯合會圓玄學院石圍角小學<br />\n<br />\nL1302和富慈善基金李宗德博士全人發展教育中心<br />\nL2802屯門紫田村村公所 <br />\nL3002福亨村村公所 <br />\n<br />\nM1102瑋琦文化教育機構(殷翠幼稚園)<br />\n<br />\nN1601打鼓嶺嶺英公立學校 <br />\nN1603*吉澳村公所 <br />\nN1604沙頭角中心小學 <br />\nN1605*李氏宗祠<br />\nN1803軍地蔬菜產銷有限責任合作社 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">P1304泰亨公立學校</span> </span><br />\nP1902*民安隊大灘營 <br />\nP1903*塔門鄉公所<br />\n<br />\nT0103*大澳䃟頭村村公所 <br />\nT0105*牛牯塱三鄉合作社 <br />\nT0106*寶蓮禪寺大澳廳 <br />\nT0109杯澳公立學校 <br />\nT0902*索罟灣普通科門診診所 <br />\n<br />\n#未有人認頭票站</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac4ce032e14fdff418935f602a5d22cf2bcfb9","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"有咩禁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(利申:真。泰亨人)"},{"pid":"dace021409cc33869c0c1cd7e3c6521828fd48f3","tid":1750290,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beac4ce032e14fdff418935f602a5d22cf2bcfb9","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"有咩禁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(利申:真。泰亨人)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"泰亨人可摸幫手影票站相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4167f4a451210e9c152a7c9a67608a0c6bff070e","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dace021409cc33869c0c1cd7e3c6521828fd48f3","tid":1750290,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beac4ce032e14fdff418935f602a5d22cf2bcfb9","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"有咩禁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(利申:真。泰亨人)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"泰亨人可摸幫手影票站相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"等陣影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f393178939265d38eb827cd205e2533b2c67f7c","tid":1750290,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4167f4a451210e9c152a7c9a67608a0c6bff070e","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dace021409cc33869c0c1cd7e3c6521828fd48f3","tid":1750290,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beac4ce032e14fdff418935f602a5d22cf2bcfb9","tid":1750290,"uid":250874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"有咩禁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(利申:真。泰亨人)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"